I am an undercover police officer.

522
00:40:42,380 --> 00:40:44,371
当然,我们是一伙的
Of course I've been with you every step of the way.

523
00:40:44,460 --> 00:40:46,815
我是说,有其他证据吗?
I mean,how else would I obtain evidence?

524
00:40:47,180 --> 00:40:49,136
你干吗不做个好姑娘呢?
Why don't you just be a good little girl,yeah?

525
00:40:49,220 --> 00:40:50,699
