I tell you what,you keep the original artwork,cover expenses.

530
00:41:09,860 --> 00:41:11,498
我们需不需要表示感谢?
Are we supposed to be grateful?

531
00:41:11,980 --> 00:41:13,811
我根本不在乎你干什么
I really don't care what you are.

532
00:41:13,900 --> 00:41:16,812
