Now I am going to walk out that door,you are going to leave it...

533
00:41:16,900 --> 00:41:19,414
10分钟,你们就自由了
ten minutes,then you're free to go.

534
00:41:19,980 --> 00:41:22,369
什么,你真以为会这样?
What,and you really think that's going to happen?

535
00:41:23,340 --> 00:41:26,537
相信我,Danny,你一点都 不适合穿监狱服,伙计
Trust me,Danny,you really wouldn't suit prison overalls,mate.

536
00:41:26,700 --> 00:41:29,168
