Max,we need one identical copy and then another copy with a small flaw.

544
00:42:16,380 --> 00:42:17,574
瑕疵?
A flaw?

545
00:42:18,420 --> 00:42:20,411
你们心里怎么想的?
What sort of thing did you have in mind?

546
00:42:21,300 --> 00:42:22,699
哦,我的天哪
Oh,my God.

547
00:42:43,740 --> 00:42:47,255
- 等等,你怎么回事,嗨? - 对不起
- Wait a minute,where are you,hello? - Sorry.

548
00:42:49,060 --> 00:42:51,130
- 哦,算了 - 对不起
- Right.Okay. - Sorry.

549
00:42:59,980 --> 00:43:01,299
Jackson小姐
Miss Jackson.

550
00:43:04,940 --> 00:43:08,569
你送来拍卖的作品事实上是赝品
It appears that the artwork you put up for sale is,in fact,a forgery.

551
00:43:08,660 --> 00:43:10,139
警察在赶来的路上
The police are on their way.

552
00:43:10,740 --> 00:43:14,176
好吧,我是Phillips警官 我在执行卧底的任务
Right.D.I.Phillips.I am working undercover.

553
00:43:14,740 --> 00:43:16,776
嫌疑犯还在里面,对吧?
The suspects are still inside,all right?

554
00:43:16,860 --> 00:43:20,455
我们以前也和警方合作过 他们都会通知我们
We've worked with the police before.They've always notified us in the past.

555
00:43:21,020 --> 00:43:25,093
- 出于手续原因,我们不能 - 我们?你的支援呢?
- We couldn't,for operational reasons. - We?Where's your backup?

556
00:43:25,460 --> 00:43:27,371
今天就我一个
I'm working on my own today.

557
00:43:28,180 --> 00:43:30,091
我们为什么不进去谈?
Why don't we discuss this inside?

558
00:43:32,700 --> 00:43:35,134
你们干什么?我是警察
What are you doing?I am a police officer.

559
00:43:35,260 --> 00:43:39,299
好样的,大个子,啊?放开我!
Feel good,big man,does it?Get your hands off me!

560
00:44:01,820 --> 00:44:03,776
Cole警官,Martin探员
D.I.Cole,this is D.S.Martin.

561
00:44:04,140 --> 00:44:08,372
在过去几个月里,我打入这群人内部
I've been working the inside with this crew for the last couple of months.

562
00:44:08,740 --> 00:44:10,935
告诉我们,你为什么要卖这件艺术品
Tell us why you put the artwork up for sale.

563
00:44:11,140 --> 00:44:12,732
艺术专家认识他们
The art expert knew them.

564
00:44:12,820 --> 00:44:15,459
这是让他们拿着它进来的唯一的办法
It was the only way I could get them to go through with it.

565
00:44:15,700 --> 00:44:18,692
听着,他们的名字是 请记住这个,行吗
Look,their names are,just remember this,all right...

566
00:44:18,780 --> 00:44:23,615
Michael Stone,Danny Blue,和Ash Morgan.去查Mickey的案底
Michael Stone,Danny Blue,and Ash Morgan.Check Mickey's record.

567
00:44:26,740 --> 00:44:30,210
好了,她的身份没错,对不起
Okay.She checks out.Sorry.

568
00:44:31,220 --> 00:44:33,575
谢谢你们,他们溜了 而我也暴露了身份
Thanks to you,they've got away,and my cover's blown.

569
00:44:33,660 --> 00:44:35,013
我又怎么会知道?
How was I to know?

570
00:44:35,100 --> 00:44:37,568
身份证和艺术品都有可能是假的
The ID and artwork could've both been forgeries.

571
00:44:37,660 --> 00:44:39,218
那么,摄像头在哪里?
So,what's the scam?

572
00:44:39,460 --> 00:44:43,976
听着,他们在展品展出的时候 把真的和假的掉了包
Look,they switched the authentic artwork for a forgery while it was on display.

573
00:44:44,340 --> 00:44:47,332
- 我知道,那这里的闭路电视呢? - 不管用的
- I take it you have CCTV here? - Won't help.

574
00:44:47,580 --> 00:44:49,457
Ash Morgan曾是个工程师
Ash Morgan posed as an engineer.

575
00:44:49,540 --> 00:44:52,213
他改装过了闭路电视 所以它什么也不会录下
He rigged the CCTV,so it recorded absolutely nothing.

576
00:44:52,780 --> 00:44:54,771
今天,我们没有请过工程师
We haven't had an engineer here today.

577
00:44:54,980 --> 00:44:58,450
我个人授权所有的维修 如果我们有,我会知道的
I personally authorize all maintenance.I would've known if we had.

578
00:45:00,420 --> 00:45:02,092
我们为什么不去看一看?
Why don't we take a look at it?

579
00:45:10,100 --> 00:45:12,534
正如我所说的,它工作正常
Like I said,it's working perfectly.

580
00:45:16,460 --> 00:45:18,769
这个男人Ash并没有离开拍卖行
This guy Ash didn't leave the auction room.

581
00:45:19,500 --> 00:45:22,492
