That's not Mr.Henshaw.Mr.Henshaw's white.

588
00:45:43,540 --> 00:45:44,689
11美元
One-ten.

589
00:45:46,780 --> 00:45:48,498
也不是另外一个
It's not the other guy,either.

590
00:45:52,860 --> 00:45:55,055
那儿,现在,我跟着他们,对吧
There,now,I follow them,okay.

591
00:45:55,260 --> 00:45:57,012
到楼梯间的摄像头
Go to the camera in the stairwell.

592
00:45:57,500 --> 00:45:59,809
楼梯间没有摄像头
There are no cameras in the stairwell.

593
00:46:03,100 --> 00:46:06,331
如果闭路电视正常 你会看到他们换画
If the CCTV's working,you will see them switch the artwork.

594
00:46:12,100 --> 00:46:15,217
没问题,他们并没有走近 黑色暴风连环画
Nope,they didn't go anywhere near the Black Storm artwork.

595
00:46:16,140 --> 00:46:18,938
等等,你知道的,他们肯定会的
Wait,you know,they must have.

596
00:46:19,860 --> 00:46:21,737
我能看到你在边上
I can see you near it.

597
00:46:24,900 --> 00:46:26,856
- 现在怎么了? - 没什么
- What's happening now? - That's nothing.

598
00:46:27,300 --> 00:46:29,291
有个孩子放了他的气球
Some kid let go of his balloons.

599
00:46:58,580 --> 00:47:02,619
那么我们唯一失去图像的时候 是你站在它边上
So the only time we lose sight of the artwork,you're standing right next to it.

600
00:47:07,060 --> 00:47:11,929
- 盒子里是什么? - 没什么,是空的
- What's in the case? - Nothing.It was empty.

601
00:47:12,020 --> 00:47:15,490
从我为他们送了画开始我就拿着它
I still had it from when I delivered the artwork for them.

602
00:47:16,180 --> 00:47:19,616
那么,我听说你的专家今天没来
So,I understand your own expert isn't in today.

603
00:47:19,740 --> 00:47:21,890
Paul?不,他今天早上打电话来请了病假
Paul?No,he called in sick this morning.

604
00:47:22,180 --> 00:47:25,650
好吧,在我检查的时候 我要你把热帽打开
Okay,I need you to turn the hot tap on in the bathroom while I check it.

605
00:47:52,500 --> 00:47:53,774
对不起,伙计
Sorry,pal.

606
00:48:01,700 --> 00:48:03,258
现在箱子在哪里?
Where's the case now?

607
00:48:04,020 --> 00:48:05,817
我把它还给Mickey和Danny
I gave it back to Mickey and Danny.

608
00:48:07,140 --> 00:48:09,700
当我们遗失画的时候Mickey 和Danny在哪里?
Where were Mickey and Danny when we lost the picture?

609
00:48:11,340 --> 00:48:14,491
在大厅,没有靠近展品黑色风暴
In the foyer,nowhere near the Black Storm artwork.

610
00:48:19,420 --> 00:48:21,695
