You do still have the banker's draft,don't you?

611
00:48:21,780 --> 00:48:23,736
是的,当然
Yeah,of course.

612
00:48:49,420 --> 00:48:53,049
那个女人,和带气球的孩子
The woman and the kid with the balloons.

613
00:48:54,380 --> 00:48:56,735
那么,这是什么?也许我们该去查查
So,what's this?Maybe we should check this out.

614
00:48:59,260 --> 00:49:00,773
