I've got other evidence.

615
00:49:02,220 --> 00:49:07,214
听着,他们在骗一个地产商 这里
Listen,they were running a con on some estate agent.Here you go.

616
00:49:07,740 --> 00:49:10,208
Richard Shaw,对吧?这就是他们骗的那个人
Richard Shaw,all right?That's the guy they were conning.

617
00:49:10,300 --> 00:49:12,609
他可以完全解释我的话
He will totally back up my story.

618
00:49:13,820 --> 00:49:17,017
你做不做傻瓜?这是2万5千镑
You'd have to be an idiot not to.25,000.

619
