Richard Shaw地产商?
Richard Shaw.Estate agent?

620
00:49:28,340 --> 00:49:29,819
我不这么认为
I don't think so.

621
00:49:36,900 --> 00:49:39,539
听着,我可以带你们去 那个伪造的工作室
Look,I can take you to the forger's studio.

622
00:49:49,700 --> 00:49:54,330
好吧,让我们来找出赝品
Okay.Let's play Spot the Forgery.

623
00:49:57,260 --> 00:49:59,615
我告诉你们了,他们把钥匙塞给我的
I told you,they planted the key on me.

624
00:49:59,700 --> 00:50:02,692
那为什么保险箱是以你的名字登记的?
How come the safe deposit box is registered in your name?

625
00:50:29,460 --> 00:50:31,576
拍卖行的地图?
Blueprints for the auction house.

626
00:50:32,820 --> 00:50:34,492
关于黑色风暴的调查
Research on Black Storm.

627
00:50:38,900 --> 00:50:40,572
而这里有1万英镑
And there's got to be 10,000 here.

628
00:50:41,060 --> 00:50:43,130
剩下的一万呢?
What happens to the other 10,000?

629
00:50:43,500 --> 00:50:44,979
好好猜猜吧
Take a wild guess.

630
00:50:49,660 --> 00:50:51,218
他们把我开到了这里
They steered me here.

631
00:50:51,300 --> 00:50:54,178
但这是你的保险箱 是你登记的
But it's your safe deposit box.It's registered to you.

632
00:50:54,260 --> 00:50:58,378
是的,但他们知道我会在 去的路上看保险箱
Yeah,but they knew I'd see the safe depository when we drove past.

633
00:50:59,980 --> 00:51:02,653
- 老实说,我们在哪里? - Manor路
- Actually,where are we? - Manor Road.

634
00:51:03,300 --> 00:51:06,258
哦,对,没错,右转
Right,yeah,it is right.Take the next right.

635
00:51:13,780 --> 00:51:15,498
他们早知道我有个保险箱在这里
They must have known I had a box here.

636
00:51:15,580 --> 00:51:17,855
那他们怎么拿到你保险箱里的东西呢?
And how would they get inside your safe deposit box?

637
00:51:59,060 --> 00:52:00,413
这个假的
It's counterfeit.

638
00:52:06,140 --> 00:52:07,653
那这是什么?
What's this,then?

639
00:52:11,820 --> 00:52:13,014
Eddie
Eddie.

640
00:52:15,260 --> 00:52:16,818
她就是那个两面派警察
She's this bent D.I.

641
00:52:17,900 --> 00:52:20,653
她抓了Billy和他手下 到这儿来赌博,你知道
She caught Billy and his crew gambling down here,you know...

642
00:52:20,740 --> 00:52:22,059
他们玩纸牌
they were playing poker.

643
00:52:22,700 --> 00:52:25,373
她要1万英镑,否则我就得丢执照
She wants 10,000,or I lose me license.

644
00:52:26,220 --> 00:52:27,972
我可能一无所有,Mick
And I could lose everything,Mick.

645
00:52:30,780 --> 00:52:33,453
- 你和我想得一样吗? - 是的
- Are you thinking what I am thinking? - Yup.

646
00:52:34,660 --> 00:52:36,013
她漂亮吗?
Is she fit?

647
00:52:43,300 --> 00:52:47,373
- 好吧,我可以带你们去他们的旅馆 - 住宾馆并没有违法
- Okay,I can take you to their hotel. - It's not illegal to stay in a hotel.

648
00:52:47,460 --> 00:52:50,497
- 是的,但我们可以搞张搜查令 - 出于什么理由?
- Yeah,but we can get a search warrant. - On what grounds?

649
00:52:50,860 --> 00:52:53,772
Mickey和Danny并没有来卖画 是你卖的
Mickey and Danny didn't put the artwork up for sale,you did.

650
00:52:54,220 --> 00:52:56,131
是你拿了银行支票
You collected the banker's draft.

651
00:52:56,740 --> 00:53:00,415
就我们所知,他们也没有调包画 而你
As far as we can tell,they didn't switch the artwork,either,whereas you....

652
00:53:01,020 --> 00:53:03,418
那是闭路电视的镜头,这是证据
There's CCTV footage,witnesses. 

653
00:53:03,419 --> 00:53:05,252
听着,所有这一切,拍品
Look,all this.Everything,the lot,okay?

654
00:53:05,340 --> 00:53:07,900
都是Mickey和Danny的
It's all Mickey and Danny.

655
00:53:07,980 --> 00:53:10,096
没有任何证据表明,你跟他们说过话
There's no evidence you even spoke to them.

656
00:53:10,260 --> 00:53:14,048
也没有所谓的伪造者Max 没有Richard Shaw
There's no Max the Forger.There's no Richard Shaw.

657
00:53:14,860 --> 00:53:17,897
Mickey和Danny没有做出 任何违法的事情
This Mickey and Danny don't appear to have done anything illegal.

658
00:53:17,980 --> 00:53:19,698
不管怎么说,至少今天没有
At least not today,anyway.

659
00:53:20,500 --> 00:53:23,298
- 而这些从哪儿来的? - 他们设计的
- Where did all this come from? - They planted it.

660
00:53:24,980 --> 00:53:29,690
- 是他们算计了我 - 你能证明吗?
- They are setting me up. - Can you prove it?

661
00:53:32,020 --> 00:53:34,011
我没有选择的余地,对不起
I don't have any choice.I'm sorry.

662
00:53:34,420 --> 00:53:39,130
Samantha Phillips,我怀疑你 涉嫌偷窃,诈骗,拘捕你
Samantha Phillips.I am arresting you on suspicion of theft,fraud,and deception.

663
00:53:40,020 --> 00:53:41,578
你可以保持沉默
You do not have to say anything...

664
00:53:41,660 --> 00:53:44,618
但这将影响你的辩护 如果你对所提问的只字不提
but it may harm your defense if you do not mention when questioned...

665
00:53:44,700 --> 00:53:46,691
这都将会是你的成堂证供
something which you later rely on in court.

666
00:53:46,780 --> 00:53:49,419
看吧,桌上的卡片
Come on,cards on the table.

667
00:53:50,100 --> 00:53:52,295
你会不会对她粗暴点?
Would you have a little knock-about with her?

668
00:53:53,900 --> 00:53:55,572
正如所说的,Danny,我很挑剔的
Like I said,Danny,I'm very choosy.

669
00:53:55,660 --> 00:53:58,015
是的,但是挑剔也没什么不好
Yeah,but choosy ain't getting you nowhere.

670
00:53:59,260 --> 00:54:02,775
尤其当她把警棍拿出来对着我的时候
When she got that truncheon out,did it for me.

671
00:54:03,300 --> 00:54:05,814
女人是氪(你克星)
Women are your kryptonite.

672
00:54:06,260 --> 00:54:09,411
你在干吗,你那是在干什么?旅游还是什么?
What are you on about,what are you on?Are you tripping or something?

673
00:54:09,500 --> 00:54:11,968
我是他们的氪 Albert,我,听着
I'm their kryptonite.Albert,I....Listen.

674
00:54:13,100 --> 00:54:16,137
- 女人对我无法抗拒 - 是的,接着做梦吧
- Women are powerless to resist me. - Yeah,dream on.

675
00:54:16,260 --> 00:54:17,932
- 好的,我来载你们 - 不,我来开
- Right,I'll drive you. - No,I'm driving.

676
00:54:18,020 --> 00:54:19,419
让我来开
Let me drive.

677
00:54:22,740 --> 00:54:24,651
你能帮我开下门吗?
Would you open the door for me,please?

678
00:54:26,380 --> 00:54:29,133
- 要让我们干所有的事情,是不是? - 谢谢
- Want us to do everything,yeah? - Thank you.

679
00:54:33,540 --> 00:54:36,691
我不想开车,行了吧?所以我骗了你,我赢了
I didn't want to drive,okay?So I tricked you,so I won.

680
00:54:36,780 --> 00:54:38,896
你开,我不开.算了吧
You drive,I am not driving.Forget it.

681
00:54:45,140 --> 00:54:46,619
等等,爸爸
But,Dad.

682
00:54:47,940 --> 00:54:50,898
- 十分荣幸 - 拿着吧,你的第一份奖金
- Always a pleasure. - Here you go,your first score.

683
00:54:51,900 --> 00:54:53,936
- 就这些? - 闭嘴
- Is that all? - Shut up.

684
00:54:54,020 --> 00:54:56,614
- 他学得很快 - 伙计们,待会见
- He's learning fast. - I'll see you around,guys.

685
00:54:58,580 --> 00:54:59,933
- 谢谢 - 很高兴跟你合作
- Thank you. - Nice working with you.

686
00:55:00,020 --> 00:55:01,658
走吧,我们回家去
Come on,let's get you home.

687
00:55:14,340 --> 00:55:17,138
- Eddie,怎么了? - 我滑了一跤
- Eddie,what happened? - I slipped.

688
00:55:19,180 --> 00:55:22,536
是的,在你来酒吧前我没时间用填充物
Yeah,I didn't have time to fit the padding before you got to the bar.

689
00:55:22,940 --> 00:55:25,170
哦,我们什么也不能说,对吧?
Yeah,I couldn't exactly say anything,could I?

690
00:55:25,260 --> 00:55:27,296
欺骗是个很危险的游戏,Eddie
Grifting's a dangerous game,Eddie.

691
00:55:27,700 --> 00:55:29,099
但从好的一面来看
But look on the bright side...

692
00:55:29,180 --> 00:55:31,648
至少Phillips警官 不会再打扰你了
at least D.I.Phillips won't be bothering you anymore.

693
00:55:32,420 --> 00:55:34,331
是得,这下好了,谢谢,伙计们
Yeah,nice one.Thanks,fellas.

694
00:55:37,660 --> 00:55:41,335
那我呢就去兑现了来自拍卖行的汇款
So,I cashed the banker's draft we got from the auction house.

695
00:55:42,500 --> 00:55:45,776
钱在这里,8万英镑
The money's in here,along with the 80,000...

696
00:55:45,860 --> 00:55:48,658
Neil很高兴能买下原稿
that Neil very happily paid for the original.

697
00:55:49,180 --> 00:55:51,091
危险,但是诱人
Dangerous,but lucrative.

698
00:55:51,180 --> 00:55:53,410
这是不是意味着你们能够结帐了?
So does this mean you lot are going to settle your tab?

699
00:55:53,500 --> 00:55:54,853
- Eddie. - 有意思
- Eddie. - Charming.

700
00:55:54,940 --> 00:55:56,612
- 你的感激之情呢? - 也不谢谢
- Where's the gratitude? - No appreciation.

701
00:55:56,700 --> 00:55:58,372
你想想我们干吗这么烦
Makes you wonder why we bother.

702
00:55:58,460 --> 00:56:00,018
好吧,这里
All right,then,here.

703
00:56:03,580 --> 00:56:05,969
好了,我搞定了
Okay then,I'd better be off.

704
00:56:06,060 --> 00:56:07,049
等等
Hold on.

705
00:56:07,420 --> 00:56:09,172
你盛装打扮要去哪里?
Where are you going all dressed up?

706
00:56:10,140 --> 00:56:14,258
我不认为这与你有关,Danny
I don't think that's,any of your business,Danny.

707
00:56:15,020 --> 00:56:17,659
- 她要去约会 约会? - 跟谁?
- She's got a date. - A date?Who with?

708
00:56:18,900 --> 00:56:21,368
我想这跟你也没有关系
I don't think that's any of your business,either.

709
00:56:21,580 --> 00:56:24,378
- Neil. - Neil,是Neil?
- Neil. - Neil.Neil?

710
00:56:25,860 --> 00:56:30,092
你要跟个连环画怪胎约会
You are going out with some specky comic-book geek,when...

711
00:56:30,420 --> 00:56:35,335
而弃像我这样英俊,善良,幽默 敏锐和有创造性的男人
a beautiful,friendly,funny,sensitive,creative guy...

712
00:56:35,420 --> 00:56:37,775
在一边?
like me doesn't even get a look in?

713
00:56:39,300 --> 00:56:41,495
就是这样,不是吗,Danny?
Looks that way.Doesn't it,Danny?

714
00:56:42,380 --> 00:56:44,848
好了,伙计们,别等太晚
Okay,guys,don't wait up.

715
00:56:46,620 --> 00:56:48,053
打牌,绅士们?
Cards,gentlemen?

716
00:56:49,140 --> 00:56:51,700
打牌?对,好主意
Cards?Yeah,brilliant.

717
00:56:53,140 --> 00:56:55,449
我简直无法抑制我的激动
I can hardly handle the excitement.

718
00:57:05,580 --> 00:57:06,569
什么?
What?

719
00:57:06,980 --> 00:57:09,494
我们说好,一把10块?
Shall we say,a tenner a hand?

720
00:57:10,580 --> 00:57:14,255
- 不,不行 - Eddie,来吧
- No.No way. - Eddie,come on.

721
00:57:14,380 --> 00:57:15,699
随便玩玩
Just a bit of fun.

722
00:57:15,940 --> 00:57:18,090
另外,你现在也是我们的一员了
Besides,you're one of the crew now.

723
00:57:22,100 --> 00:57:25,775
那么,Eddie,你什么牌?
So,Eddie,what do you got?

724
00:57:29,420 --> 00:57:30,819
以为我会告诉你?
Like I'd tell you lot.

